        I came across this grove of palm trees in Arashiyama today, and although it's only a few degrees above freezing, I feel like I'm in Hawaii!
</p>

<p class="jp">
        今日は嵐山でこのヤシの木立に出くわした。気温は氷点下数度しかないが、まるでハワイにいるような気分だ！
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Trees" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[I came across this grove of palm trees in Arashiyama today, and although it's only a few degrees above freezing, I feel like I'm in Hawaii!]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2502_IMG_1026.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2502_IMG_1026.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Harukas in the Clouds・雲の上のハルカス</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250213/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Harukas in the Clouds・雲の上のハルカス" /><published>2025-02-13T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-02-13T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/harukas</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250213/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
       Clouds reflect in the window while shooting the Abeno Harukas tower. the tallest building in Kansai.
</p>

<p class="jp">
        あべのハルカスを撮影中、窓に雲が映り込んだ。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Osaka" /><category term="Architecture" /><category term="Art" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Clouds reflect in the window while shooting the Abeno Harukas tower. the tallest building in Kansai.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2502_A7R01544_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2502_A7R01544_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Piétons・歩行者</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250212/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Piétons・歩行者" /><published>2025-02-12T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-02-12T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/osaka-station</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250212/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
       Above Osaka Station, looking down over one of the many pedestrian walkways, in the light rain.
</p>

<p class="jp">
        小雨が降る中、大阪駅の上空から歩行者用通路のひとつを見下ろす。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Osaka" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Street" /><category term="Trains" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Above Osaka Station, looking down over one of the many pedestrian walkways, in the light rain.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2502_A7R01498_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2502_A7R01498_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Kyoyochi Pond・鏡容池</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250211/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kyoyochi Pond・鏡容池" /><published>2025-02-11T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-02-11T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/ryoanji-pond</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250211/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
